BlockSource: http://www.rsssf.com/tablesc/cidades16.html
Competition: Torneio das 4 Cidades 
Season: 1916

*Organized in 1916 by Sport Lisboa e Benfica;
*all games in Campo de Sete Rios, in Lisbon.

Round: 1
1/1/1916 Racing Madrid;   1-3; Montriond-Sport de Lausanne ; Campo de Sete Rios, Lisbon
1/1/1916 SL Benfica;      9-0; FC Porto; Campo de Sete Rios, Lisbon

Round: 2
1/2/1916 Montriond-Sport; 6-0; FC Porto; Campo de Sete Rios, Lisbon
1/2/1916 SL Benfica     ; 5-0; Racing Madrid; Campo de Sete Rios, Lisbon

Round: Final
1/4/1916; SL Benfica     ; 3-1; Montriond-Sport; Campo de Sete Rios, Lisbon
      
*NB: Montriond were making an Iberian Trip 1916.
   
